Tutorial for how to use VICON positioning system with a Pixhawk6C. Useful for MSc students in Cranfield. 

There are still many things I didn't to dicuss on this guide... 
If you are enthuesastic about not having others suffer from the same problem you faced, or believe the doucmentation could've been better,
please fork this depositionary request to pull! 

The main.tex is a latex file that you can edit, bibliography is in the .bib file, and all images are located within the images folder.

